WEBVTT

00:02.127 --> 00:03.878
[melodic whistling]

00:03.961 --> 00:04.421
[smacking]

00:04.504 --> 00:05.588
[exhaling deeply]

00:05.672 --> 00:08.090
thump!
both: WHOA!

00:08.173 --> 00:10.802
- ♪ HERE WE GO 'CAUSE WE'RE
FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:10.885 --> 00:12.303
♪ A LITTLE CUCKOO,
FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:12.387 --> 00:13.763
♪ WE'RE AMAZING
TOTALLY CRAZY ♪

00:13.847 --> 00:14.764
♪ FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:14.848 --> 00:16.306
♪ COME ON, EVERYBODY, SING ♪

00:16.391 --> 00:17.934
♪ WE'RE GONNA SCREAM
AT THE TOP OF OUR LUNGS ♪

00:18.017 --> 00:19.602
♪ WE'RE GONNA FLY
AND HAVE SOME FUN ♪

00:19.686 --> 00:21.646
♪ WE DON'T CARE IF YOU STARE ♪

00:21.730 --> 00:22.605
♪ OR EVEN
LOOK AT OUR UNDERWEAR ♪

00:22.689 --> 00:25.066
both: ♪ BRAIN ♪

00:25.150 --> 00:27.110
♪ FREEZE ♪

00:27.193 --> 00:28.361
♪ OOH ♪

00:28.445 --> 00:29.696
♪ BRAIN FREEZE! ♪

00:29.779 --> 00:31.448
- ♪ BUH-BUH, BAH,
BAH, BAH, BAH, BAH, BAH ♪

00:31.531 --> 00:33.450
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH, BAH-BAH,
BUH, BAH-BAH, BAH ♪

00:33.533 --> 00:34.784
♪ BAH, BAH, BAH, BAH ♪

00:34.868 --> 00:35.952
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH-BAH,
BUH-BAH, BAH ♪

00:36.035 --> 00:37.871
♪ COME AND SCREAM
AT THE TOP OF YOUR LUNGS ♪

00:37.954 --> 00:40.290
♪ COME AND FLY
AND HAVE SOME FUN ♪

00:40.373 --> 00:41.291
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH ♪

00:41.374 --> 00:42.751
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH ♪

00:42.834 --> 00:44.252
♪ BUH-BUH, BAH, BAH,
FANBOY AND CHUM CHUM ♪

00:44.335 --> 00:45.462
both: OH!
- THAT'S NICE.

00:47.046 --> 00:50.049
{\an8}[ominous music]

00:50.133 --> 00:55.722
{\an8}♪ ♪

00:57.348 --> 00:59.476
[doorbell rings]

00:59.559 --> 01:02.145
- UGH.

01:02.228 --> 01:05.022
ALL RIGHT, I'M COMING.

01:05.105 --> 01:09.152
DID NOT REALIZE
MY LEGS WERE STILL ASLEEP.

01:09.235 --> 01:11.488
[thunder crackles]

01:11.571 --> 01:13.490
A COFFIN?

01:13.573 --> 01:15.325
WELL, THAT'S STRANGE.

01:15.408 --> 01:16.993
HMM.
NO CARD.

01:17.076 --> 01:18.745
OOF!

01:18.828 --> 01:20.371
[grunts]

01:22.081 --> 01:24.209
AW, I ALREADY HAVE ONE OF THESE.

01:25.585 --> 01:27.545
[cracking]

01:29.255 --> 01:29.631
- [hisses]

01:29.714 --> 01:33.218
- [screams]

01:33.301 --> 01:33.676
- [yawns]

01:33.760 --> 01:36.179
MORNING, FANBOY.

01:36.262 --> 01:38.640
- CHUM CHUM,
I HAD THE CRAZIEST DREAM.

01:38.723 --> 01:40.225
- THE ONE WHERE YOU STAND
IN FRONT OF A CROWD

01:40.308 --> 01:41.559
WITHOUT YOUR UNDERWEAR?

01:41.643 --> 01:43.686
- NO, I DREAMT I WAS BIT
BY A VAMP--

01:43.770 --> 01:45.897
WAIT A MINUTE.

01:45.980 --> 01:47.273
CHUM CHUM,
WHAT IS THIS ON MY NECK?

01:50.610 --> 01:51.236
- HMM.

01:51.319 --> 01:54.072
LOOKS LIKE A MOSQUITO BITE.

01:54.155 --> 01:55.198
- OR...

01:55.281 --> 01:57.659
A VAMPIRE BITE.

01:57.742 --> 01:58.910
- WHAT?

01:58.993 --> 01:59.953
- THINK ABOUT IT.

02:00.036 --> 02:01.704
IT WAS A HOT MUGGY NIGHT,

02:01.788 --> 02:03.206
WE SLEPT WITH THE WINDOW OPEN,

02:03.289 --> 02:04.707
AND NOW I HAVE A BUMP ON MY NECK

02:04.791 --> 02:09.044
THAT IS SWOLLEN AND ITCHY.

02:09.127 --> 02:11.464
DOES THAT SOUND LIKE
A MOSQUITO BITE TO YOU?

02:11.548 --> 02:13.091
- HMM...
- YES.

02:13.174 --> 02:14.592
YES.

02:14.676 --> 02:17.262
I CAN ALREADY FEEL
THE VAMPIRE BLOOD

02:17.345 --> 02:20.223
COURSING THROUGH MY VEINS.

02:20.306 --> 02:21.558
- OOH! OOH!

02:21.641 --> 02:23.726
CAN I BE YOUR SLIGHTLY DERANGED,
BUG-EATING SIDEKICK?

02:23.810 --> 02:25.562
- MMM,
HOW'S YOUR CREEPY GIGGLE?

02:25.645 --> 02:29.315
- [giggles maniacally]

02:29.816 --> 02:31.526
- WELCOME ABOARD.

02:31.609 --> 02:33.278
thud!

02:36.114 --> 02:38.283
- REMIND ME THAT I HAVE TO STOP
BY WIZARD CO.

02:38.366 --> 02:39.993
I NEED TO GET SOME WAND POLISH.

02:40.076 --> 02:41.536
THEN I HAVE TO GO AND GET--

02:41.619 --> 02:42.537
[record scratches]

02:42.620 --> 02:44.205
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

02:44.289 --> 02:45.206
- UH, SLEEPING?

02:45.290 --> 02:49.335
IT'S WHAT WE VAMPIRES DO
DURING THE DAY.

02:49.419 --> 02:51.254
- YOU'RE A VAMPIRE?

02:51.337 --> 02:54.382
WHAT DO THEY CALL YOU,
COUNT DORKULA?

02:54.465 --> 02:56.384
[chuckles]

02:56.467 --> 02:58.970
- [giggles]

02:59.053 --> 03:04.517
MAY I INTRODUCE YOU
TO MY VAMPIRE MASTER,

03:04.601 --> 03:07.061
COUNT FANG-BOY?

03:07.145 --> 03:08.938
- GOOD EVENING.

03:09.022 --> 03:10.315
AH!

03:10.398 --> 03:11.983
MY BALANCE IS A LITTLE OFF.

03:12.066 --> 03:15.695
I FLEW OVER HERE,
AND MY EARS HAVEN'T POPPED YET.

03:15.778 --> 03:16.696
BLEH.

03:16.779 --> 03:17.780
BLEH.

03:17.864 --> 03:19.449
BLEE.
BLEH.

03:19.532 --> 03:22.327
- YOU ARE NOT A VAMPIRE.

03:22.410 --> 03:24.704
IF YOU WERE,
THE SUNLIGHT WOULD DESTROY YOU.

03:24.787 --> 03:25.788
- BLEH.

03:25.872 --> 03:27.582
AH!
THE SUNLIGHT!

03:27.665 --> 03:29.542
TOUCHING MY VAMPIRE SKIN.

03:29.626 --> 03:32.378
[screams]

03:32.462 --> 03:33.546
IT BURNS.

03:33.630 --> 03:35.506
IT BURNS.

03:35.590 --> 03:36.674
BLEH!

03:36.758 --> 03:38.176
TODAY WAS SUPPOSED TO BE
OVERCAST.

03:38.259 --> 03:42.847
CURSE YOU,
CHANNEL 5 WEATHER CENTER.

03:42.931 --> 03:46.976
YOU'VE TURNED ME TO DUST.

03:47.060 --> 03:49.395
- YOU'RE NOT A VAMPIRE,

03:49.479 --> 03:50.939
AND THANK GOODNESS.

03:51.022 --> 03:51.898
THE VERY THOUGHT
OF AN IMMORTAL FANBOY

03:51.981 --> 03:54.692
IS ALMOST TOO MUCH TO BEAR.

03:54.776 --> 03:56.152
- IMMORTAL.

03:56.235 --> 03:58.613
OOH, I LIKE THE SOUND OF THAT.

03:58.696 --> 03:59.989
I JUST WISH I KNEW
WHAT IT MEANT.

04:00.073 --> 04:00.990
- [sighs]

04:01.074 --> 04:03.076
IT MEANS THAT YOU LIVE FOREVER.

04:03.159 --> 04:05.286
READ A BOOK SOMETIME,
WHY DON'T YOU?

04:05.370 --> 04:07.288
SCRIVENER ELF, WALK WITH ME.

04:07.372 --> 04:08.706
- WOW.

04:08.790 --> 04:11.000
I'M GONNA LIVE FOREVER?

04:11.084 --> 04:12.877
COOL!

04:12.961 --> 04:15.630
- [cries]

04:15.713 --> 04:18.298
- CHUM CHUM?

04:18.382 --> 04:20.843
CHUM CHUM, WHAT'S THE MATTER?

04:20.927 --> 04:24.514
- YOU'RE GONNA LIVE FOREVER
WITHOUT ME,

04:24.597 --> 04:28.309
AND YOU DON'T EVEN CARE!

04:28.393 --> 04:29.394
- WHAT?

04:29.477 --> 04:31.688
I NEVER THOUGHT OF THAT.

04:31.771 --> 04:35.400
I DON'T WANT TO LIVE FOREVER IF
MY BEST FRIEND WON'T BE WITH ME.

04:35.483 --> 04:36.776
OH, MAN.

04:36.859 --> 04:41.030
THIS HAS TOTALLY HARSHED
MY VAMPIRE MELLOW.

04:41.114 --> 04:44.158
- IT'S KILLING
MY ASSISTANT BUZZ TOO.

04:44.242 --> 04:45.201
- WAIT A MINUTE!

04:45.284 --> 04:46.744
I'VE GOT IT!

04:46.828 --> 04:48.538
WHAT IF I BITE YOUR NECK,

04:48.621 --> 04:50.248
AND THEN YOU'D BECOME A VAMPIRE
TOO,

04:50.331 --> 04:52.417
AND WE'D BOTH LIVE FOREVER
TOGETHER.

04:52.500 --> 04:54.961
- YOU'D DO THAT FOR ME?

04:55.044 --> 04:56.963
- OF COURSE, BUDDY.

04:59.215 --> 05:00.800
- AH...

05:00.883 --> 05:01.759
HMM?

05:01.843 --> 05:03.094
AH, CHUM CHUM.

05:03.177 --> 05:04.887
AM I MISSING SOMETHING

05:04.971 --> 05:07.181
OR ARE YOU MISSING SOMETHING?

05:07.265 --> 05:08.683
WHERE'S YOUR NECK?

05:08.766 --> 05:11.394
- I ALWAYS FIGURED IT WOULD
GROW IN DURING HIGH SCHOOL.

05:11.477 --> 05:13.813
NOW WE CAN'T BE IMMORTAL
TOGETHER

05:13.896 --> 05:16.482
BECAUSE I'M A NECK-LESS FREAK!

05:16.566 --> 05:18.359
[sobs]

05:19.986 --> 05:22.947
- DON'T YOU WORRY, BUDDY,

05:23.031 --> 05:25.867
BECAUSE WE ARE GOING TO GET YOU
A NECK.

05:25.950 --> 05:29.704
[thunder crackles]

05:29.787 --> 05:31.956
"CERTIFIED NECK SPECIALIST.

05:32.040 --> 05:33.249
"EVENINGS ONLY.

05:33.332 --> 05:34.375
WALK-INS WELCOME."

05:34.459 --> 05:35.418
COME ON, CHUM CHUM.

05:35.501 --> 05:37.754
I GOT A GOOD FEELING ABOUT THIS.

05:37.837 --> 05:40.048
[door creeks]

05:42.633 --> 05:44.218
[whimpering]

05:44.302 --> 05:47.305
[ominous organ music]

05:47.388 --> 05:52.310
♪ ♪

05:52.393 --> 05:54.437
- GOOD EVENING.

05:54.520 --> 05:56.689
- [slurping]

05:59.192 --> 06:02.111
- I DID NOT HEAR YOU COME IN.

06:02.195 --> 06:04.781
I GAVE MY ASSISTANT JANICE
THE NIGHT OFF.

06:04.864 --> 06:05.656
I AM

06:05.740 --> 06:09.160
DR. ACULA!

06:09.243 --> 06:12.288
- UH, IT SAYS <i> COUNT</i> DR. ACULA
ON YOUR DIPLOMA.

06:12.371 --> 06:13.289
- DOES IT?

06:13.372 --> 06:18.711
OH, YES.
I MINORED IN ACCOUNTING.

06:22.673 --> 06:23.966
NOW, WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU,

06:24.050 --> 06:27.136
MY CHILDREN OF THE NIGHT?

06:27.220 --> 06:28.387
- OKAY.

06:28.471 --> 06:29.889
I KNOW THIS IS GOING TO SOUND
A LITTLE CRAZY,

06:29.972 --> 06:31.933
BUT HERE GOES.

06:32.016 --> 06:34.644
I AM A VAMPIRE.

06:34.727 --> 06:36.646
- [spits]
A VAMPIRE?

06:36.729 --> 06:38.147
- PLEASE DON'T BE FRIGHTENED.

06:38.231 --> 06:40.691
YOU ARE IN NO DANGER.

06:40.775 --> 06:43.111
BUT YOU MIGHT WANT TO WEAR
THIS GARLIC NECKLACE.

06:43.194 --> 06:45.113
- [screams]

06:45.196 --> 06:48.324
I MEAN, THAT IS VERY SHOCKING,

06:48.407 --> 06:51.410
BUT I AM SURE YOU COULDN'T
POSSIBLY HURT ME.

06:51.494 --> 06:54.580
YOU SEEM LIKE A VERY NICE
VAMPIRE.

06:54.664 --> 06:55.414
- SO NICE THAT HE WANTS
TO BITE ME

06:55.498 --> 06:59.502
AND MAKE ME HIS IMMORTAL
COMPANION,

06:59.585 --> 07:01.379
BUT FIRST I NEED A NECK.

07:01.462 --> 07:05.007
- OH, HOW ADORABLE.

07:05.091 --> 07:10.096
YOU WANT A NECK SO YOU CAN BE
BITTEN BY A VAMPIRE.

07:10.179 --> 07:13.683
I THINK I CAN HELP YOU
WITH THAT.

07:19.981 --> 07:23.860
NOW, YOU MIGHT FEEL
A LITTLE PRESSURE.

07:23.943 --> 07:25.027
crunch!

07:25.111 --> 07:29.073
JUST ONE LAST BANDAGE...

07:29.157 --> 07:30.491
[chuckles]

07:30.575 --> 07:31.492
AND THERE.

07:34.036 --> 07:34.871
- OOH!

07:34.954 --> 07:36.122
HOW DOES IT LOOK?

07:36.205 --> 07:40.835
- IT'S...

07:40.918 --> 07:44.380
MAGNIFICENT.

07:44.463 --> 07:47.967
- HEY, CHUM CHUM,
HOW DID IT TURN OUT?

07:48.050 --> 07:48.885
- OOH.

07:48.968 --> 07:51.053
IT'S SO SLENDER.

07:51.137 --> 07:53.389
- YOU DO SOME FINE WORK, DOC.

07:53.472 --> 07:54.891
- [muffled]
THANK YOU.

07:54.974 --> 07:55.641
- OOH! OOH!

07:55.725 --> 07:57.226
HAVE YOU TRIED SWALLOWING YET?

07:57.310 --> 07:58.269
HERE, EAT THIS!

07:58.352 --> 07:59.395
EAT THIS!

07:59.478 --> 08:01.856
- [grunts]

08:02.732 --> 08:04.942
MY ARMS DON'T REACH MY MOUTH
ANYMORE,

08:05.026 --> 08:06.319
BUT I DON'T CARE.

08:06.402 --> 08:07.653
[giggles]

08:07.737 --> 08:09.906
OOH, I HAVE A NECK!

08:09.989 --> 08:12.742
- NOW IT'S MY VAMPIRE DUTY
TO BITE IT

08:12.825 --> 08:14.994
AND MAKE YOU IMMORTAL.

08:15.077 --> 08:16.245
BLEH.

08:16.329 --> 08:17.288
- DON'T TOUCH HIM!

08:17.371 --> 08:18.623
HE'S MINE!

08:18.706 --> 08:19.790
I MEAN...

08:19.874 --> 08:23.085
WOULD YOU MIND FILLING OUT
SOME PAPERWORK?

08:23.169 --> 08:25.338
AND JUST SIGN HERE.

08:25.421 --> 08:25.838
AND HERE.

08:25.922 --> 08:28.633
AND...

08:28.716 --> 08:30.760
- LOOK, CHUM CHUM.
A SUNLAMP.

08:30.843 --> 08:32.220
- [screams]

08:32.303 --> 08:34.054
- NOW YOU WON'T HAVE THOSE
TAN LINES ON YOUR NEW NECK.

08:34.138 --> 08:35.932
ARE YOU OKAY, DOCTOR?

08:36.015 --> 08:38.183
- COULD YOU HAND ME
THAT ALOE VERA?

08:38.267 --> 08:39.393
[gasps]

08:39.477 --> 08:41.854
IT'S ALMOST SUNRISE!

08:41.938 --> 08:45.483
- AND NOW TO MAKE YOU
MY ETERNAL IMMORTAL COMPANION

08:45.566 --> 08:46.984
FOREVER!

08:47.068 --> 08:50.112
TILL THE END OF TIME.

08:50.196 --> 08:51.197
- NO!

08:51.280 --> 08:52.281
- [giggling]
IT TICKLES.

08:52.365 --> 08:54.700
YOUR MOUTH FEELS LIKE A PUPPY.

08:54.784 --> 08:56.619
- OKAY, YOU'VE HAD YOUR FUN.

08:56.702 --> 08:59.664
WE DON'T WANT TO BRUISE
THAT NECK NOW, HUH?

08:59.747 --> 09:01.123
- WHY CAN'T YOU KEEP STILL?

09:01.207 --> 09:03.626
- [stammering]

09:03.709 --> 09:06.462
AH, ENOUGH OF THIS!

09:06.545 --> 09:08.631
- UH, FANBOY?

09:08.714 --> 09:09.757
- OH, THAT'S BETTER.

09:09.840 --> 09:10.299
NOW, JUST TURN A LITTLE MORE

09:10.383 --> 09:12.468
TO THE SI-I-I-IDE!

09:12.551 --> 09:14.971
- NOW I WILL SHOW YOU HOW
TO BITE A NECK.

09:15.054 --> 09:17.265
- UH, OKAY.

09:17.348 --> 09:19.141
AND HOW WOULD <i> YOU</i> KNOW?

09:19.225 --> 09:20.476
- YOU FOOLS.

09:20.559 --> 09:22.937
I AM A VAMPIRE!

09:23.020 --> 09:26.732
AND YOU ARE MY NEXT VICTIM.

09:26.816 --> 09:27.942
AHH!

09:28.025 --> 09:29.652
thud!

09:29.735 --> 09:33.322
- IF ANYONE IS GONNA SNACK
ON MY BEST FRIEND,

09:33.406 --> 09:34.657
IT'S GOING TO BE ME.

09:34.740 --> 09:35.908
- [screams]

09:35.992 --> 09:38.536
[smacking]

09:38.619 --> 09:39.954
WAIT A MINUTE.

09:40.037 --> 09:41.664
THAT TASTE.

09:41.747 --> 09:43.958
WHY IS IT SO FAMILIAR?

09:44.041 --> 09:45.042
COULD I HAVE BITTEN YOU BEFORE?

09:45.126 --> 09:47.211
- NOPE.

09:47.295 --> 09:49.338
THE VAMPIRE WHO BIT ME
ONLY HAD ONE FANG.

09:49.422 --> 09:51.799
SEE?

09:51.882 --> 09:55.094
- YOU'RE RIGHT.
I DID NOT MAKE THAT BITE.

09:55.177 --> 09:56.137
A MOSQUITO DID.

09:56.220 --> 09:58.180
- REALLY?
HUH.

09:58.264 --> 09:59.223
- YOU IDIOT!

09:59.307 --> 10:01.684
I MADE THIS BITE.

10:01.767 --> 10:03.352
[dog howls]

10:03.436 --> 10:04.270
- WOW.

10:04.353 --> 10:05.521
DO NOT KNOW HOW I MISSED THAT.

10:05.604 --> 10:09.525
- BITING YOU MADE ME
GOOFY-HEADED ALL DAY!

10:09.608 --> 10:11.402
ALL I WANTED TO DO WAS PLAY
VIDEO GAMES

10:11.485 --> 10:14.989
AND DRINK
THE FROSTY FREEZY FREEZE.

10:16.615 --> 10:17.908
AND I COULDN'T STOP PASSING GAS.

10:17.992 --> 10:21.162
[farts]

10:21.245 --> 10:22.538
- SORRY,
I MISSED THAT LAST PART.

10:22.621 --> 10:24.957
- AND NOW I'VE BITTEN YOU AGAIN!

10:25.041 --> 10:28.002
I CAN ALREADY FEEL
YOUR IDIOT BLOOD

10:28.085 --> 10:30.296
DULLING MY BRAIN.

10:30.379 --> 10:31.797
UGH!

10:31.881 --> 10:34.592
I'VE GOT TO GET TO MY COFFIN
WHILE I STILL CAN.

10:34.675 --> 10:35.634
AH!

10:35.718 --> 10:36.677
UGH!

10:36.761 --> 10:37.762
MY EYE!

10:37.845 --> 10:38.387
UGH!

10:38.471 --> 10:40.181
AH!
THE MORNING SUN!

10:40.264 --> 10:42.808
IT'S DESTROYING ME!

10:42.892 --> 10:45.227
UGH!

10:45.311 --> 10:48.022
TELL JANICE TO CANCEL MY 3:00!

10:48.105 --> 10:49.690
[screams]

10:49.774 --> 10:52.276
poof!

10:52.360 --> 10:54.070
- I GUESS THAT EXPLAINS
HIS SUBSCRIPTION

10:54.153 --> 10:57.740
TO <i> BATTY HOMES AND GUANO.</i>

10:57.823 --> 10:59.075
[farting sound]

10:59.158 --> 11:00.451
- OOF.

11:00.534 --> 11:03.871
THAT SECOND BITE
REALLY GAVE ME A HEADACHE.

11:03.954 --> 11:06.082
- YOU NEED TO TAKE TWO BITES,

11:06.165 --> 11:07.958
AND CALL ME IN THE MORNING.

11:08.042 --> 11:10.002
[laughs]

11:11.462 --> 11:12.588
- [hisses]

11:12.671 --> 11:13.923
- IS THIS GONNA HURT?

11:14.006 --> 11:14.507
chomp!

11:14.590 --> 11:18.177
[ominous organ music]

11:18.260 --> 11:19.011
♪ ♪

11:19.095 --> 11:21.806
ding-dong!

11:21.889 --> 11:24.934
- HAVEN'T SEEN YOU TWO TWERPS
HERE FOR DAYS.

11:25.017 --> 11:26.394
[chuckles]

11:26.477 --> 11:27.436
- YES.

11:27.520 --> 11:29.939
WE'RE MORE NIGHT PEOPLE NOW.

11:30.022 --> 11:33.317
ISN'T THAT RIGHT,
MY IMMORTAL COMPANION?

11:33.401 --> 11:36.112
- RIGHT, FANG-BOY.

11:37.196 --> 11:39.240
thud!

11:39.323 --> 11:40.116
[hissing]

11:40.199 --> 11:41.283
- NOT COOL, GUYS.

11:41.367 --> 11:42.993
chomp! chomp!

11:43.077 --> 11:45.663
[screams]

11:46.330 --> 11:48.124
{\an8}- ♪ MONSTER ♪

11:48.207 --> 11:50.292
{\an8}♪ A MONSTER IN THE MIST ♪

11:50.376 --> 11:53.629
{\an8}♪ I SAW A MONSTER ♪

11:53.712 --> 11:55.673
{\an8}♪ A MONSTER IN THE MIST ♪

11:56.799 --> 11:58.217
- BOOP, BOOP, BOOP.
BEE, BOOP, BOOP.

11:58.300 --> 12:00.511
- ROBO-FANBOY,

12:00.594 --> 12:03.347
WHAT IS THIS STRANGE
EARTH OBJECT?

12:03.431 --> 12:05.182
- BOOP, BEE, BOOP, BOOP.

12:05.266 --> 12:07.226
[monotone]
MAYBE IT IS A HOT DOG.

12:08.018 --> 12:10.271
UGH.

12:10.354 --> 12:13.065
IT IS NOT A HOT DOG.

12:13.149 --> 12:16.902
[laughter]

12:16.986 --> 12:17.278
- CHOMP IT, MINI CHIMP.

12:17.361 --> 12:19.155
- [gasps]

12:19.238 --> 12:19.989
- OH, NO.
IT'S BOOG.

12:20.072 --> 12:21.198
I FORGOT HE WALKS TO WORK
THIS WAY.

12:21.282 --> 12:23.993
- HE'S GONNA BOP US!

12:24.076 --> 12:25.995
HE ALWAYS BOPS US!

12:26.078 --> 12:27.663
- SORRY, LOSERS.
NO CAN DO THIS TIME.

12:27.746 --> 12:29.165
I'M IN THE MIDDLE
OF MY LONGEST-EVER GAME

12:29.248 --> 12:31.333
OF <i> MINI CHOMP.</i>

12:31.417 --> 12:32.168
MINI CHOMP!

12:32.251 --> 12:33.836
CHOMP, CHOMP, CHOMP, CHOMP,
CHOMP!

12:33.919 --> 12:34.795
[chuckles]

12:34.879 --> 12:35.838
POW! POW!

12:35.921 --> 12:37.006
[laughs]

12:37.089 --> 12:39.258
CHOMP IT.

12:39.341 --> 12:41.177
- MY TUMMY HURTS.

12:41.260 --> 12:44.263
- CHUM CHUM, YOU JUST NEED
TO GET BOOG OFF YOUR MIND.

12:44.346 --> 12:46.348
IF ONLY THERE WAS SOMETHING FUN
WE COULD DO...

12:46.432 --> 12:48.934
- FROSTY MART.

12:49.018 --> 12:50.603
FROSTY MART.

12:50.686 --> 12:51.937
- HEY, IT'S LENNY!

12:53.772 --> 12:55.024
both:
♪ MY MOTHER AND YOUR MOTHER ♪

12:55.107 --> 12:56.859
♪ WERE OUT HANGING CLOTHES ♪

12:56.942 --> 12:58.944
♪ MY MOTHER POKED YOUR MOTHER
RIGHT IN THE NOSE ♪

12:59.028 --> 13:00.362
- HEY!

13:00.446 --> 13:02.281
DON'T YOU DING-A-LINGS
HAVE ANYTHING BETTER TO DO?

13:02.364 --> 13:04.533
- THAN THIS?

13:04.617 --> 13:05.534
both: OOH!

13:05.618 --> 13:06.535
OOH!

13:06.619 --> 13:07.244
- YEAH, RIGHT.

13:07.328 --> 13:08.370
OH, YEAH.

13:08.454 --> 13:11.207
UH-HUH.
UH-HUH.

13:11.290 --> 13:13.751
- HEY, SWEET MOVES, BRO.

13:13.834 --> 13:14.960
- THANKS.

13:15.044 --> 13:17.046
I CALL IT
"THE CHUM CHUM CHA-CHA".

13:17.129 --> 13:19.173
- OW!
I GOTTA LEARN THAT.

13:19.256 --> 13:21.425
LET'S GRAB SNACKS
AT THE FROSTY MART

13:21.509 --> 13:23.719
SO WE CAN SPEND ALL DAY
OUT HERE.

13:23.802 --> 13:24.094
- YES!

13:24.178 --> 13:27.056
- NO!

13:27.139 --> 13:29.058
I HATE MY JOB.

13:30.809 --> 13:31.685
ding-dong!

13:31.769 --> 13:34.522
- HE'S STILL PLAYING HIS GAME.

13:34.605 --> 13:36.315
- HEY, GOOD NEWS.

13:36.398 --> 13:37.650
I'M ON THE FINAL LEVEL.

13:37.733 --> 13:39.818
I'LL BE BOPPING YOU
IN TWO SHAKES.

13:39.902 --> 13:40.945
[laughs]

13:41.028 --> 13:41.278
- [gasps]

13:41.362 --> 13:42.905
YIKES!

13:42.988 --> 13:44.448
WE GOTTA MAKE THIS QUICK!

13:47.409 --> 13:48.118
- COME ON. COME ON.
COME ON.

13:48.202 --> 13:49.119
- GOT IT.

13:49.203 --> 13:51.121
- GO! GO!

13:51.205 --> 13:52.206
SNACKS, SNACKS, SNACKS.

13:52.289 --> 13:53.415
- INSTANT MASHED POTATOES?

13:53.499 --> 13:54.124
- WANT IT!

13:54.208 --> 13:55.668
- YOGURT-COVERED PORK RINDS?

13:55.751 --> 13:56.585
- NEED IT!

13:56.669 --> 13:57.920
- GRANNY BRAN CEREAL!

13:58.003 --> 14:01.715
- THE DISGUSTING CEREAL
WITH AWESOME PRIZES.

14:01.799 --> 14:06.262
- I'M ALMOST OUT OF CHIMPS
TO CHOMP!

14:06.345 --> 14:09.640
- I'LL MAKE IT FAST.

14:09.723 --> 14:10.808
- CHIMPITY, CHIMPITY, CHOMP.

14:10.891 --> 14:11.850
OH, YEAH.

14:11.934 --> 14:13.102
GAME OVER.

14:13.185 --> 14:14.436
IT WAS TOTALLY WORTH
STARING AT A TINY SCREEN

14:14.520 --> 14:17.439
FOR TWO AND A HALF DAYS.

14:17.523 --> 14:18.941
HMM.

14:19.024 --> 14:22.111
FOR SOME REASON MY PEEPERS
AIN'T WORKING SO GOOD.

14:22.194 --> 14:26.448
LUCKY FOR ME, MY BOPPING HAND'S
GOT BUILT-IN DWEEB SENSORS.

14:26.532 --> 14:27.449
- [panting]

14:27.533 --> 14:28.158
- SEEK AND BOP, FISTY.

14:28.242 --> 14:30.286
COME ON.

14:30.369 --> 14:32.079
OOH,
YOU CAN DO IT.

14:32.162 --> 14:33.789
- [barks]

14:33.872 --> 14:34.206
- HURRY!
HURRY!

14:34.290 --> 14:36.667
- [barks]

14:36.750 --> 14:38.377
- OOH!

14:38.460 --> 14:39.128
ATTABOY!

14:39.211 --> 14:42.423
WHO'S A GOOD FIST, HMM?
HMM?

14:42.506 --> 14:43.632
- [growls]

14:43.716 --> 14:45.509
- [screams]

14:45.593 --> 14:48.137
- WHY DIDN'T HE BOP US?

14:48.220 --> 14:49.930
- HE'S A COMPLICATED GUY.

14:50.014 --> 14:52.474
- [whimpering]

14:52.558 --> 14:54.143
WHERE IS HE?

14:54.226 --> 14:54.768
WHERE'D HE GO?

14:54.852 --> 14:55.936
- WHO?
- THE MONSTER!

14:56.020 --> 14:58.981
THERE'S A BIG, HONKING MONSTER
IN HERE

14:59.064 --> 15:00.316
EVEN HUGER THAN ME,

15:00.399 --> 15:02.026
AND I'M HUGE.

15:02.109 --> 15:04.278
both: A MONSTER?

15:04.361 --> 15:05.988
AWESOME!

15:09.658 --> 15:10.951
- AW, POO.

15:11.035 --> 15:11.660
HE RAN OFF.

15:11.744 --> 15:13.454
- WELL, DON'T HOLD OUT ON US.

15:13.537 --> 15:17.499
WHAT DID HE LOOK LIKE?

15:17.583 --> 15:20.753
- HE HAD--HE HAD FOUR CREEPY
ARMS, RIGHT?

15:20.836 --> 15:24.048
- FOR SQUEEZING YOUR GUTS OUT.

15:24.131 --> 15:25.424
- gulp!

15:25.507 --> 15:28.093
COLD BEADY EYES
THAT LOOKED RIGHT THROUGH ME.

15:28.177 --> 15:31.430
- SO HE CAN PICK WHICH ORGAN
TO EAT FIRST.

15:31.513 --> 15:32.431
WAIT A MINUTE.

15:32.514 --> 15:33.724
WAS HIS MOUTH
BIG ENOUGH TO EAT YOUR HEAD?

15:33.807 --> 15:35.726
- ACTUALLY, YOU KNOW WHAT IT
WAS--

15:35.809 --> 15:37.353
WHY ARE YOU ASKING ME THAT?

15:37.436 --> 15:38.646
- 'CAUSE IT SOUNDS A LOT LIKE
THE MONSTER IN THAT MOVIE

15:38.729 --> 15:42.191
<i>MONSTER IN THE MIST.</i>

15:42.274 --> 15:44.360
- I REMEMBER THAT.

15:44.443 --> 15:47.780
[creepily]
THE MIST.

15:47.863 --> 15:51.033
- MAYBE THIS IS THE SAME KIND
OF MONSTER.

15:51.116 --> 15:51.909
HMM?

15:51.992 --> 15:53.202
- I DOUBT IT.

15:53.285 --> 15:54.078
IN THE MOVIE,
THE MONSTER ONLY SHOWED UP

15:54.161 --> 15:56.538
WHEN THERE WAS A THICK,
CREEPY MIST.

15:56.622 --> 15:59.708
- LIKE THAT?

15:59.792 --> 16:01.126
- YUP, THAT'S THE ONE.

16:01.210 --> 16:02.711
[screams]

16:04.546 --> 16:06.173
- THE MONSTER!

16:06.256 --> 16:06.548
both: THE MONSTER?

16:06.632 --> 16:08.592
[screams]

16:08.676 --> 16:10.302
- [whimpering]

16:10.386 --> 16:10.928
- WAIT!

16:11.011 --> 16:12.596
WHERE DID THE MONSTER GO?

16:12.680 --> 16:13.514
- I GUESS HE WENT BACK INTO

16:13.597 --> 16:17.518
[creepily]
THE MIST.

16:17.601 --> 16:18.560
- BUT WHAT IF IT DIDN'T?

16:18.644 --> 16:19.895
WHAT IF HE'S HIDING?

16:19.978 --> 16:21.563
WHAT IF HE JUMPS OUT
AND SWALLOWS MY HEAD

16:21.647 --> 16:23.315
LIKE A BIG BONELESS MEATBALL?

16:23.399 --> 16:24.233
- I KNOW!

16:24.316 --> 16:26.151
WE'LL DO WHAT THEY DID
IN THE MOVIE.

16:26.235 --> 16:28.404
THEY WALKED AROUND ALL SLOW
AND QUIET TILL THE MONSTER

16:28.487 --> 16:29.405
JUMPED OUT!

16:29.488 --> 16:31.824
- [screams]

16:31.907 --> 16:32.574
- AND STARTED CHASING THEM.

16:32.658 --> 16:34.535
- [whimpering]

16:34.618 --> 16:35.744
- THEN THEY LED HIM TO THE DOOR,

16:35.828 --> 16:36.704
PUSHED HIM OUT, AND LOCKED IT.

16:36.787 --> 16:38.580
- I DON'T IF I CAN DO THAT.

16:38.664 --> 16:39.623
I'M SCARED.

16:39.707 --> 16:40.708
AND LAZY.

16:40.791 --> 16:42.376
- NO SWEAT.
WE GOT YOU COVERED.

16:42.459 --> 16:45.170
- IT'S EASY WHEN YOU'RE TRAINED
AND EQUIPPED.

16:45.254 --> 16:47.256
[heavy metal music]

16:47.339 --> 16:55.222
♪ ♪

16:57.307 --> 16:58.225
[gunshots]

17:00.561 --> 17:01.770
- [screams]

17:01.854 --> 17:03.105
WAIT, ARE YOU NUTS?

17:03.188 --> 17:05.148
WE CAN'T DEFEND OURSELVES
WITH HOT SNACKS

17:05.232 --> 17:05.898
AND PLASTIC CUTLERY.

17:05.983 --> 17:08.359
- THAT'S WHY WE'RE ALSO EQUIPPED

17:08.444 --> 17:10.529
WITH THE ONLY EFFECTIVE
MONSTER POISON KNOWN TO MAN.

17:10.612 --> 17:13.824
- SPRAY CHEESE.

17:13.906 --> 17:16.117
- SO POWERFUL,
ONE NACHOFUL COULD WIPE OUT

17:16.201 --> 17:18.287
AN ENTIRE MONSTER POOL PARTY.

17:18.369 --> 17:20.247
♪ ♪

17:20.329 --> 17:23.291
LOCK AND LOAD, PEOPLE.

17:23.375 --> 17:25.461
- LET'S DO THIS THING.

17:25.544 --> 17:27.755
♪ ♪

17:29.673 --> 17:32.342
- HE'S GONNA JUMP OUT AND BOP ME
ANY MINUTE.

17:32.426 --> 17:33.343
I'M FREAKING HERE!
I'M--

17:33.427 --> 17:35.220
- SHH!

17:35.304 --> 17:36.472
[rumbling]

17:36.555 --> 17:38.265
- [whimpers]

17:43.020 --> 17:44.354
[screams]

17:45.731 --> 17:46.732
- STOP IT!

17:46.815 --> 17:48.442
BOOG, IT'S ME!

17:48.525 --> 17:50.235
- HEY, THE MONSTER SOUNDS
LIKE LENNY.

17:50.319 --> 17:52.154
- KINDA LOOKS LIKE HIM TOO.

17:52.237 --> 17:52.654
- KEEP SPRAYING!
KEEP SPRAYING!

17:52.738 --> 17:55.157
- USE YOUR EYES!

17:55.240 --> 17:55.824
UGH.

17:55.908 --> 17:58.744
WHAT ARE YOU IDIOTS DOING?

17:58.827 --> 18:00.871
WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU PEOPLE?

18:00.954 --> 18:02.039
smack!

18:02.122 --> 18:03.832
- THERE'S A MONSTER
ON THE LOOSE.

18:03.916 --> 18:07.503
- JUST LIKE IN
<i>MONSTER IN THE MIST.</i>

18:07.586 --> 18:09.755
- [creepily]
THE MIST.

18:09.838 --> 18:11.507
- THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

18:11.590 --> 18:12.508
- HE SAW IT.

18:12.591 --> 18:14.676
IT'S HUGE.

18:14.760 --> 18:15.677
- YEAH, HUGE.

18:15.761 --> 18:18.222
I'VE NEVER BEEN SO SCARED!

18:18.305 --> 18:20.182
SPEAKING OF,
I GOTTA HIT THE BATHROOM

18:20.265 --> 18:22.434
AND RINSE OUT A FEW THINGS,
ALL RIGHT?

18:22.518 --> 18:24.561
- WOULD YOU PLEASE BRING ME
SOMETHING

18:24.645 --> 18:27.856
TO WIPE THE CHEESE OUT
OF MY EYES?

18:27.940 --> 18:29.149
HMM?

18:29.233 --> 18:30.067
- TISSUES.

18:30.150 --> 18:31.443
RIGHT AWAY, SIR.

18:31.527 --> 18:33.987
STEADY, FANBOY.

18:34.071 --> 18:35.364
- HUH.

18:35.447 --> 18:37.699
HUH?

18:37.783 --> 18:39.034
- [growls]

18:39.117 --> 18:40.369
- [screams]

18:40.452 --> 18:41.954
THE MONSTER!

18:42.037 --> 18:43.455
both: THE MONSTER?

18:43.539 --> 18:44.706
[screams]

18:44.790 --> 18:47.209
- [screams]

18:47.292 --> 18:48.210
WAIT, DID I JUST HEAR--

18:48.293 --> 18:49.878
AH, THE MONSTER!

18:49.962 --> 18:50.379
both: THE MONSTER?

18:50.462 --> 18:53.048
[screams]

18:54.132 --> 18:55.926
- AW, HE'S GONE.

18:56.009 --> 18:58.345
- OFF TO VISIT HIS NANA IN

18:58.428 --> 19:01.473
[creepily]
THE MIST.

19:01.557 --> 19:03.058
- BUT HE'LL KEEP COMING BACK.

19:03.141 --> 19:04.226
I CAN'T DEAL WITH THIS HERE.

19:04.309 --> 19:06.520
WE GOTTA BARRICADE OURSELVES IN
FOREVER!

19:06.603 --> 19:08.772
- IN THE MOVIE, THEY PUT
SANDBAGS IN THE WINDOWS.

19:08.856 --> 19:10.691
- THAT WAS COOL.
LET'S DO THAT.

19:10.774 --> 19:12.442
- YEAH, THEN WE CAN ALL LIVE
HERE.

19:12.526 --> 19:14.570
WE'LL SLEEP ON THE FLOOR
AND EAT SNACKS.

19:14.653 --> 19:15.904
- LIKE CAMPING,
BUT WITHOUT THE BORING.

19:15.988 --> 19:17.489
- 'CAUSE THERE'S A MONSTER
AFTER US.

19:17.573 --> 19:20.117
[giggles]

19:20.200 --> 19:22.202
- [whimpers]

19:23.829 --> 19:24.830
- WELL, WE DIDN'T HAVE SANDBAGS,

19:24.913 --> 19:26.290
SO I USED SOUR CREAM AND ONION,

19:26.373 --> 19:29.167
AND I PUT ELECTRIC BARS
ON THE BACK DOOR.

19:29.251 --> 19:30.335
zap!

19:30.419 --> 19:31.837
- IT'S ALL RIGHT,

19:31.920 --> 19:33.130
BUT THE ONLY THING MAKING ME
FEEL SAFE

19:33.213 --> 19:35.257
IS OUR STOCKPILE
OF MONSTER-STOPPING CHEESE

19:35.340 --> 19:36.258
OVER THERE.

19:36.341 --> 19:38.260
- [clears throat]

19:38.343 --> 19:42.764
MAY I PRESENT,
LORD AND LADY CHEESINGTON.

19:42.848 --> 19:45.225
- CHARMED, I'M SURE.

19:45.309 --> 19:46.727
- THERE'S A MONSTER
ON THE LOOSE,

19:46.810 --> 19:49.605
AND YOU WASTED ALL OUR CHEESE?

19:49.688 --> 19:50.898
- WE'RE ALL GONNA DIE,

19:50.981 --> 19:53.442
AND YOU TWO ARE GOING FIRST!

19:53.525 --> 19:54.610
- THERE'S NO TIME FOR BOPPING.

19:54.693 --> 19:58.530
SOMEBODY'S GOT TO GO OUT THERE
AND GET US MORE CHEESE.

19:58.614 --> 19:59.948
- OH, NO.
NOT ME.

20:00.032 --> 20:01.116
NO, I'M STAYING RIGHT HERE
WHERE IT'S SAFE.

20:01.199 --> 20:03.827
- HEY, THAT'S WHAT THAT GUY SAID
IN THE MOVIE.

20:03.911 --> 20:04.786
- WHICH GUY?

20:04.870 --> 20:06.121
- THE GUY WHO GOT EATEN.

20:06.204 --> 20:08.248
ding!

20:08.332 --> 20:10.208
- SO WHILE I'M OUT HERE
GETTING US MORE CHEESE,

20:10.292 --> 20:12.085
IF I GET INTO TROUBLE,
I YANK ON THE ROPE,

20:12.169 --> 20:15.047
AND YOU PULL ME BACK
QUICK AS YOU CAN, RIGHT?

20:15.130 --> 20:15.964
- RIGHT.

20:16.048 --> 20:17.382
- OKAY, AND IF YOU GET EATEN?

20:17.466 --> 20:19.259
BEFORE HE SWALLOWS YOU,

20:19.343 --> 20:21.887
DO ME A SOLID AND TOSS THE ROPE
OUT THE DOOR.

20:22.721 --> 20:24.973
ding-dong!

20:29.019 --> 20:32.230
I'M OUTTA HERE, SUCKERS.

20:32.314 --> 20:33.273
[laughs]

20:35.859 --> 20:36.735
- [gasps]

20:36.818 --> 20:37.778
LOOK AT THE ROPE!

20:37.861 --> 20:39.279
- THE MONSTER'S AFTER HIM.

20:39.363 --> 20:41.031
together: PULL!

20:41.114 --> 20:42.532
- AH!

20:42.616 --> 20:44.326
UGH!

20:44.409 --> 20:46.119
[screams]

20:46.203 --> 20:48.121
AH!

20:48.205 --> 20:49.164
DOH!
UGH!

20:49.247 --> 20:50.165
ding-dong!

20:50.249 --> 20:51.667
- THIS IS AWESOME.

20:51.750 --> 20:54.461
WE PULLED HIM IN,
JUST LIKE IN THE MOVIE.

20:54.544 --> 20:56.380
- BUT IN THE MOVIE,
WHEN THEY PULLED HIM IN

20:56.463 --> 20:57.839
THERE WAS NOTHING LEFT
BUT A FOOT.

20:57.923 --> 20:58.840
- AH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

20:58.924 --> 21:00.133
LET'S THROW HIM BACK OUT.

21:00.217 --> 21:02.010
- AH!
LET ME GO!

21:03.512 --> 21:04.429
- OH!

21:04.513 --> 21:05.514
- OH!

21:05.597 --> 21:08.350
- UGH!
- UGH!

21:08.433 --> 21:09.518
- [grunts]

21:09.601 --> 21:09.893
- HUH?

21:09.977 --> 21:10.686
- [growls]

21:10.769 --> 21:11.687
- AH!

21:11.770 --> 21:14.106
THE MONST--

21:16.733 --> 21:18.276
- [growls when in focus]

21:22.823 --> 21:24.074
- WHAT?

21:24.157 --> 21:25.033
WAIT A--

21:25.117 --> 21:26.618
[whistle]

21:26.702 --> 21:28.036
YOU LITTLE DWEEBS.

21:28.120 --> 21:30.622
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT,
BOO--

21:30.706 --> 21:32.040
[screams]

21:32.124 --> 21:33.875
THE MONSTER!

21:33.959 --> 21:34.876
- THERE AIN'T NO MONSTER.

21:34.960 --> 21:36.545
IT'S THOSE TWO IDIOTS.

21:36.628 --> 21:37.879
- HUH?

21:37.963 --> 21:39.089
- SO WAIT A MINUTE.

21:39.172 --> 21:40.841
ALL THIS TIME
WE WERE THE MONSTER?

21:40.924 --> 21:42.676
- I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

21:42.759 --> 21:44.302
- I KNOW.

21:44.386 --> 21:45.971
IT'S EXACTLY LIKE THAT OTHER
MOVIE.

21:46.054 --> 21:48.265
both: <i> MY MONSTER, MYSELF!</i>

21:48.348 --> 21:50.017
- OOH, REMEMBER THAT PART
WHERE--

21:50.100 --> 21:51.143
- OH, YEAH.

21:51.226 --> 21:54.521
THE BIG, ANGRY GUY
BOPPED THE DUMB KIDS?

21:54.604 --> 21:55.731
- HMM.

21:55.814 --> 21:57.149
DOESN'T RING A BELL.

21:57.232 --> 21:59.026
- LOOK OUT!

21:59.109 --> 21:59.735
- [screams]

21:59.818 --> 22:02.654
- [growls]

22:06.950 --> 22:08.410
- WHAT DWEEBS.

22:08.493 --> 22:11.038
TRYING TO CONVINCE ME
THERE'S A MONSTER.

22:11.121 --> 22:12.748
PLEASE.

22:12.831 --> 22:14.791
- UH, BOOG?

22:14.875 --> 22:16.084
- FORGET IT.

22:16.168 --> 22:18.211
I AIN'T FALLING FOR IT
THIS TIME.

22:18.295 --> 22:20.672
- THERE REALLY IS A MONSTER.

22:22.340 --> 22:24.593
chomp!

22:24.676 --> 22:25.427
- HUH!

22:28.555 --> 22:30.098
- THIS BELONG TO YOU?

22:30.182 --> 22:30.766
- UM...

22:30.849 --> 22:33.268
YEAH?

22:33.351 --> 22:35.645
- I FOUND IT IN THE TRASH,
SO I THOUGHT I'D DROP IT BY.

22:35.729 --> 22:36.855
- OH.

22:36.938 --> 22:37.689
THANKS?

22:37.773 --> 22:39.733
GREAT.

22:39.816 --> 22:41.443
I THOUGHT I GOT RID OF
THIS THING.

22:41.526 --> 22:42.819
- WHY DON'T YOU PUT IT IN

22:42.903 --> 22:43.653
[creepily]
THE MIST.

22:43.737 --> 22:45.530
- HEY!

22:46.114 --> 22:51.495
[melodic whistling]

22:51.578 --> 22:54.122
- WHOA!

22:55.457 --> 22:58.543
[quirky electronic music]

22:58.627 --> 22:59.878
♪ ♪

22:59.961 --> 23:03.715
[melodic whistling]

23:03.799 --> 23:11.681
♪ ♪

